        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "## Independent Literature Sources\n\n**68 independent publications** have reported stability constants for the Cd²⁺–Cl⁻ system, spanning over six decades from **1930** (Righellato & Davies, `30RD`) to **1993** (Ghandour et al., `93GA`; Visic et al., `93VJ`). Experimental techniques include potentiometry (EMF, ion-selective electrodes, polarography), ion exchange, chromatography, and spectrophotometry.",
