        "paragraph_index": 2,
        "text": "## Species & Stability Constant Ranges\n\nThe database contains **30 measurements** across three cumulative formation equilibria, all reported at **25 °C**:\n\n| Species | Equilibrium | log β range | Ionic strength range (M) | No. of log K entries |\n|---------|-------------|-------------|--------------------------|----------------------|\n| CdCl⁺ (ML) | Cd²⁺ + Cl⁻ ⇌ CdCl⁺ | **1.35 – 1.98** | 0 – 4 | 7 |\n| CdCl₂ (ML₂) | Cd²⁺ + 2 Cl⁻ ⇌ CdCl₂ | **1.70 – 2.60** | 0 – 4 | 6 |\n| CdCl₃⁻ (ML₃) | Cd²⁺ + 3 Cl⁻ ⇌ CdCl₃⁻ | **1.50 – 2.80** | 0 – 4 | 5 |\n\nThermodynamic data (ΔH, ΔS) are also available at selected ionic strengths (0.5 and 3 M).",
